title: #BlackMarket - CapWay Mobile Bank's Sheena Allen with Chico Bean and Karlous Miller
itunes:title: #BlackMarket - CapWay Mobile Bank's Sheena Allen with Chico Bean and Karlous Miller
description:
Check out Sheena Allen's mobile bank Capway. CapWay is a digital bank providing financial access and opportunities for everyone - especially those who have been under-served, overlooked, and misunderstood by the traditional banking system. In addition to their debit card and banking features, they also offer financial content to help you grow your knowledge about money.


"Starting a bank account is just the starting point of the financial race. Achieving financial health and generational wealth is a marathon, not a sprint. At CapWay, our purpose is to make sure you have everything you need to complete the race." - Sheena Allen


https://capway.com/
